    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a Restaurateur in <strong>Restaurant Owner</strong>—a Prologue version of the full game, offering a taste of the immersive simulation experience. In this introductory chapter, you'll learn the basics of managing your own restaurant by creating unique burger recipes, unlocking new ingredients, and ensuring customer satisfaction. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Serve customers, increase your Restaurant Level, and unlock new ingredients to create unique recipes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/a7eefd62ab236bffd8ebf301c3737f70.avif?t=1733489624\" width=560 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/976201f19303a6b28bf5a1a0bf74c2c5.poster.avif?t=1733489624\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/976201f19303a6b28bf5a1a0bf74c2c5.webm?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/976201f19303a6b28bf5a1a0bf74c2c5.mp4?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create your own recipes, add them to your menu, and set prices. Be creative and use all the ingredients to fulfill your customers' needs and ensure they leave your restaurant happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/aedda9feaac880de661e5be589cad8d1.avif?t=1733489624\" width=560 height=117 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/8b7f6335782baee2bfb8d4734ab4484a.poster.avif?t=1733489624\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/8b7f6335782baee2bfb8d4734ab4484a.webm?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/8b7f6335782baee2bfb8d4734ab4484a.mp4?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage the day-to-day operations of your restaurant. Take orders, serve a diverse menu, and ensure that your customers leave satisfied.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/b4542ac915484fe23f70fa0490f46838.avif?t=1733489624\" width=560 height=117 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/dea008c84da609438d2c8ad6edf6e420.poster.avif?t=1733489624\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/dea008c84da609438d2c8ad6edf6e420.webm?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153960/extras/dea008c84da609438d2c8ad6edf6e420.mp4?t=1733489624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to turn your restaurant dreams into reality? <strong>Restaurant Owner: Prologue</strong> offers a rich and rewarding gameplay experience for simulation enthusiasts and aspiring restaurateurs, with more to come in the full version. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* <i>Note: This is a Prologue version of <strong>Restaurant Owner</strong> and is still in active development. As such, all images, information, and features described on this store page are subject to change as the game continues to evolve.</i></p>",
